<Link id="l00319" /><CodeLine lineNumber="319" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#ad40e05cea8e86b8cb58336bf87d0c89b"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">static</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">bool</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#ad40e05cea8e86b8cb58336bf87d0c89b">isSameValue</a>(</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#abf56a02cd18e783e040dc0e258deb1f9">APSInt</a> &amp;I1, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#abf56a02cd18e783e040dc0e258deb1f9">APSInt</a> &amp;I2) &#123;</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00323" /><CodeLine lineNumber="323"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Compare underlying values of two numbers.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00324" /><CodeLine lineNumber="324" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#a46be5bb239b3fc96e2ff377081579f72"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">static</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">int</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#a46be5bb239b3fc96e2ff377081579f72">compareValues</a>(</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#abf56a02cd18e783e040dc0e258deb1f9">APSInt</a> &amp;I1, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apsint/#abf56a02cd18e783e040dc0e258deb1f9">APSInt</a> &amp;I2) &#123;</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00327" /><CodeLine lineNumber="327"></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00329" /><CodeLine lineNumber="329"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (I1.getBitWidth() &gt; I2.<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/apint/#a512fe2c15ea651294688eeec1341644c">getBitWidth</a>())</span></CodeLine>
